 the university and its employees and retirees ensuring all benefit plans and services are in compliance with governing laws and regulations communicating the benefit plans in a way that promotes understanding and appreciation for the value delivered providing a robust collection of resources and information to encourage self service where appropriate service results october december 2011 health & welfare scrp tda goal actual goal actual percent of calls answered in 30 seconds 80 96 85 100 problem solved during first contact 85 97 70 69 problem resolved within five days 90 99 95 100 caller satisfaction 85 90 80 93 mybenefits log onto mybenefits to enroll change or update your benefit plans home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
